        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Rail Passenger Fairness Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the National Railroad Passenger Corporation (Amtrak) to bring a civil action in a U. S. District Court to enforce its preference rights over freight transportation in using a rail line, junction, or crossing.</p>]]>
